    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "WHEREAS the Chemical Engineering Students’ Society (ChESS) has submitted a written request for an advance to support participation in the 2025 Canadian Chemical Engineering Conference, as outlined in the attached letter;\nWHEREAS Section 6.5.3 of the Sub-Association Policy permits Sub-Associations to request advances of up to two semesters’ expected disbursements, provided sufficient funds are available and a written justification is given;\nWHEREAS based on current 2024-2025 enrolment figures, ChESS is projected to receive approximately $2,378.87 in fall and winter levy disbursements this year;\nBE IT RESOLVED THAT the Officers approve an advance of $2,300 to ChESS, pursuant to the Sub-Association Policy, to be deducted from future levy disbursements.",
    "meeting_date": "2025-08-28",
    "meeting_date_display": "Aug 28, 2025"
  },
